{"type":null,"faqId":38989,"title":"如何防止手环上的个人数据丢失？","answer":"<p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-indent:24.0pt;\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">手环本身可以保存</span><span style=\"\nfont-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">7</span><span style=\"\nfont-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">天数据，建议用户每天同步一次，同步到云上。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-indent:24.0pt;\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">手环可通过云服务同步保存您的个人数据。同步数据之前，请确保以下几点：</span><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">）您已安装最新的手环</span><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">APP</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">版本；</span><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">）手环和手机通过蓝牙正常连接；</span><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">）手环和手机电量充足。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;text-indent:24.0pt;\nline-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">请按照如下步骤同步数据：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\n\"><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\"><span>1.<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">打开手环</span><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\">APP</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">，</span><span style=\"\nline-height:150%;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">点击</span><img style=\"vertical-align:middle;\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150908084843219001.png\"><span style=\"line-height:\n150%;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif'\"><span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">进入手环设置菜单</span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">，点击“登录”，选择任一方式登录。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\n\"><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\"><span>2.<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span></span><span style=\"\nline-height:150%;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">登录后，在“华为穿戴”界面下，下拉界面更新数据。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:21.0pt;text-align:center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';layout-grid-mode:both;\n\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150908084844977002.png\" style=\"width:81.75pt;height:122.25pt\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\n\"><span style=\"font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\"><span>3.<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span></span><span style=\"\nline-height:150%;font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\n\">使用其他手机登录相同账号即可同步云终端数据。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;line-height:normal;\ntext-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other\"><b><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">说明：</span></b></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\nline-height:normal;\ntext-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other\"><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">中途更换账号会导致数据被保存在不同的两个账号下，可能造成您的数据不一致。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:150%;text-autospace:none;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';layout-grid-mode:line;margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\nline-height:normal;\ntext-autospace:ideograph-numeric ideograph-other\"><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">手环电量耗尽自动关机时，若长时间放置可能会引发数据丢失，故手环低电时请及时充电。</span></p>\n<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4299","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441673017000,"seriesProductName":"B0-Honor","visitedTimes":34,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}